'''帶鏈甲'''（{{lang-en|Banded mail}}）有三種形式，第一種是結合了羅馬{{link-en|片板甲|Lorica segmentata}}與[[板鏈甲|板鏈甲]]的複合式[[盔甲|盔甲]]；第二種是由條帶組成的鎧甲；第三種是由[[革|革]]帶補強的鏈甲。

帶鏈甲的歷史是有爭議的。雖然被確定過存在於十九世紀<ref>{{cite book | last = Fairholt| first = Frederick William | authorlink = | coauthors = | title = Costume in England: A History of Dress to the End of the Eighteenth Century | publisher = G. Bell and Sons | year = 1885 | location =  | url = http://books.google.com/?id=scwDAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA27&lpg=PA27&dq=%22banded+mail%22+history | doi = | id = | isbn =| page = 27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Hewitt | first = John | authorlink = | coauthors = Claude Blair | title = Ancient Armour and Weapons in Europe: From the iron period of the northern nations to the end of the seventeenth century | publisher = John Henry and James Parker | year = 1860 | location =  | url = http://books.google.com/?id=gUW7Kz9ylKkC&pg=PA268&dq=%22banded+mail%22+history | doi = | id = | isbn =| page = 268 }}</ref>，但後來的書籍宣稱帶鏈甲的產生是因為對中世紀藝術手法的誤解。<ref>{{cite book | last = Blair | first = Claude | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = European Armour circa IO66 to circa 1700 | publisher = THE MACMILLAN COMPANY | year = 1959 | location = New York | pages = 35–36 | url = http://www.13c.ru/texts/blair.pdf | doi =  | id =  | isbn =  | access-date = 2011-10-11 | archive-date = 2019-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190819073832/http://www.13c.ru/texts/blair.pdf }}</ref>

